{"id": "1524673055094214688", "channel_id": "1524673055094214688", "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "content": "⏰ **预售时间**\n<t:1783742400:f>\n\n🛒 **购买方式**\n✦ 方式1：前往淘宝搜索并进入「灵犀互娱官方旗舰店」 - 点击店铺首页的商品图跳转前往商品界面 - 预售开启之后即可进行购买\n\n✦ 方式2：复制链接到浏览器中打开 - 登录淘宝账号进入商品详情界面 - 预售开启之后即可进行购买\nhttps://c.tb.cn/h.RysuwD5qYaorENR?tk=EbLigoakxWf\n\n🛍️ **周边详情**\n✦ 售卖方式\n单个镭射票盲盒包含「普通版」镭射票×4、「稀有版」镭射票×1，款式互不重复。盲盒共有116种掉落组合。\n\n✦ 款式设计\n一共有58款图案，设计由背面与正面组成（背面为命轮，正面为与命轮有关的唤醒体或角色立绘），其中有4款包括了两个角色差异版本。每款均分为「普通版」与「稀有版」两个版本，共计124种设计。\n\n💡 **更多商品信息、盲盒概率说明请查看长图。**\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\n⏰ **Pre-order Time**\n<t:1783742400:f>\n\n🛒 **How to Purchase**\nCopy the link and open it in your browser. Log in to your Taobao account to access the product details page. You can purchase the product once the pre-order begins.\nhttps://c.tb.cn/h.RysuwD5qYaorENR?tk=EbLigoakxWf\n\n🛍️ **Merch Details**\n✦ Available Formats\nEach Ticket blind box contains 4 × \"Standard Edition\" tickets and 1 × \"Rare Edition\" ticket, with no duplicate designs. There are 116 possible combinations in total.\n\n✦ Design Details\nA total of 58 designs. Each design consists of a front and a back side—the back displays a WoD, while the front features the illustration of the Awakener or character related to that WoD. Among these, 4 designs include two different character variations. Each design comes in two versions: \"Standard\" and \"Rare\", totaling 124 variations.\n\n💡 **The current product details page may not be refreshed, so please refer to the long image for accurate product information.**", "timestamp": "2026-07-09T07:06:23.390000+00:00", "pinned": true, "thread_id": "1524673055094214688", "reactions": [{"emoji": "IMG_20251113_181453", "emoji_id": "1448240235757568133", "count": 3}, {"emoji": "Aurita_please", "emoji_id": "1356053110375714817", "count": 11}, {"emoji": "Doll_fail", "emoji_id": "1356083552923422770", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "GDoll_serenity", "emoji_id": "1468257540809822302", "coun